<item>
            <title>[SPARK-18121]  Unable to query global temp views when hive support is enabled. </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-18121</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Querying on a global temp view throws Table or view not found exception when Hive support is enabled. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Testcase to reproduce the problem: &lt;br/&gt;
The test needs to run when hive support is enabled.  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;  test(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;query global temp view&quot;&lt;/span&gt;) {
    val df = Seq(1).toDF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;i1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
    df.createGlobalTempView(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;tbl1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
    checkAnswer(spark.sql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;select * from global_temp.tbl1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;), Row(1))
    spark.sql(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;drop view global_temp.tbl1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
  }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cause:&lt;br/&gt;
HiveSessionCatalog.lookupRelation does not check for the global temp views. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
